        IF WS-CO-NUMBER = 1
           GO TO SURFPMGEM-010.
        IF WS-CO-NUMBER = 3
           GO TO SURFPMGEM-020.
        IF WS-CO-NUMBER = 7
           GO TO SURFPMGEM-030.
        IF WS-CO-NUMBER = 8
           GO TO SURFPMGEM-040.
           
       GO TO SURFPMGEM-999.
       SURFPMGEM-010.
      * FOR CTJ LEAVING MOST THINGS AS DEFAULT
          MOVE CONCATENATE('python MailGunEmail.py ', 
